(62, 31, 'SHOCK HIDRATACION PROFUNDA', 'It is a treatment that moisturizes the hair strand whose symptoms are damage and split ends. Contains Panthenol that helps moisturize and leave hair softer, stronger and shinier.\r\n\r\nINSTRUCTIONS FOR USE: We suggest the use of the Deep Hydration Shock Treatment twice a week during the first month; then use 1 seminal vial.\r\n1.-Wash the hair with shampoo and dry with a towel. 2.-Pour a dose of the Deep Hydration shock in 60mL of water. 3.-Mix until obtaining a soft and smooth cream. 4.-Apply it by spreading it on the hair from the middle to the end, until it is completely distributed. Let act for 5 to 10 minutes. 5.-Rinse gently with plenty of water and comb as usual.\r\nINGREDIENTS: ALCOHOL, CETYL ALCOHOL, Cetrimonium CHLORIDE, LAURYL ALCOHOL, PROPYLENE GLYCOL, Myristyl Alcohol, Quaternium-70, FRAGRANCE (PARFUM), ETHYLHEXYL METHOXYCINNAMATE, MENTHOL, ETHYLHEXYL SALICYLATE, Placental PROTEIN, BUTYL METHOXYDIBENZOYLMETHANE, CITRIC ACID HEXYL cinnamal, butylphenyl methylpropional , LINALOOL, BENZYL SALICYLATE, LIMONENE (D-LIMONENE), BLUE 1 (CI 42090).\r\n\r\nPRESENTATION: Box x 12 und – 15ml each.', 'en'),
(63, 32, 'SHOCK NUTRUCION PROFUNFA', 'Es un tratamiento capilar intensivo, contiene Proteína de Leche que nutre, humecta y restaura profundamente al cabello frágil y desvitalizado brindándole espesor, brillo y elasticidad. Con este tratamiento el cabello recupera textura, vida y luminosidad. \r\n\r\nMODO DE USO: Se sugiere el uso del Tratamiento Shock Nutrición Profunda 2 veces a la semana durante el primer mes; luego utilizar 1 ampolla seminal. \r\n1.-Lavar el cabello con shampoo y secar con una toalla. 2.-Vierta una dosis del shock Hidratación Profunda en 60mL de agua. 3.-Mezcle hasta obtener una crema suave y tersa. 4.-Aplique esparciéndola en el cabello de medios a punta, hasta lograr su total distribución. Deje actuar de 5 a 10 minutos. 5.-Enjuague suavemente, con abundante agua y proceda con el peinado en forma habitual.\r\nINGREDIENTES: ALCOHOL, CETYL ALCOHOL, CETRIMONIUM CHLORIDE, LAURYL ALCOHOL, PROPYLENE GLYCOL, MYRISTYL ALCOHOL, QUATERNIUM-70, FRAGRANCE (PARFUM), ETHYLHEXYL METHOXYCINNAMATE, ETHYLHEXYL SALICYLATE, HYDROLYZED MILK PROTEIN, BUTYL METHOXYDIBENZOYLMETHANE, CITRIC ACID, HEXYL CINNAMAL, BUTYLPHENYL METHYLPROPIONAL, LINALOOL, BENZYL SALICYLATE, LIMONENE (D-LIMONENE), YELLOW 5 (CI 19140).\r\n\r\nPRESENTACIÓN: Caja x 12 und – 15ml c/u.', 'es'),
(64, 32, 'SHOCK NUTRUCION PROFUNFA', 'It is an intensive hair treatment, it contains Milk Protein that deeply nourishes, moisturizes and restores fragile and devitalized hair, giving it thickness, shine and elasticity. With this treatment the hair recovers texture, life and luminosity.\r\n\r\nINSTRUCTIONS FOR USE: It is suggested to use the Deep Nutrition Shock Treatment twice a week during the first month; then use 1 seminal vial.\r\n1.-Wash the hair with shampoo and dry with a towel. 2.-Pour a dose of the Deep Hydration shock in 60mL of water. 3.-Mix until obtaining a soft and smooth cream. 4.-Apply it by spreading it on the hair from the middle to the end, until it is completely distributed. Let act for 5 to 10 minutes. 5.-Rinse gently with plenty of water and comb as usual.\r\nINGREDIENTS: ALCOHOL, CETYL ALCOHOL, Cetrimonium CHLORIDE, LAURYL ALCOHOL, PROPYLENE GLYCOL, Myristyl Alcohol, Quaternium-70, FRAGRANCE (PARFUM), ETHYLHEXYL METHOXYCINNAMATE, ETHYLHEXYL SALICYLATE, HYDROLYZED MILK PROTEIN, BUTYL METHOXYDIBENZOYLMETHANE, CITRIC ACID HEXYL cinnamal, butylphenyl methylpropional, LINALOOL, BENZYL SALICYLATE, LIMONENE (D-LIMONENE), YELLOW 5 (CI 19140).\r\n\r\nPRESENTATION: Box x 12 und – 15ml each.', 'en'),
(65, 33, 'SHOCK REPARACIÓN INTENSA', 'Es un tratamiento capilar intensivo para cabellos dañados o maltratados. Humecta y acondiciona profundamente el cabello, facilitando el peinado aportando brillo y suavidad. Gracias a la Proteína de Placenta reduce la formación de puntas quebradizas y previene el daño producido por los rayos solares, la salinidad, el medio ambiente y por el excesivo calor proporcionado por el secado, planchado y alisado.\r\n\r\nMODO DE USO: Se sugiere el uso del Tratamiento Shock Reparación Intensa 2 veces a la semana durante el primer mes; luego utilizar 1 ampolla seminal. \r\n1.-Lavar el cabello con shampoo y secar con una toalla. 2.-Vierta una dosis del shock Hidratación Profunda en 60mL de agua. 3.-Mezcle hasta obtener una crema suave y tersa. 4.-Aplique esparciéndola en el cabello de medios a punta, hasta lograr su total distribución. Deje actuar de 5 a 10 minutos. 5.-Enjuague suavemente, con abundante agua y proceda con el peinado en forma habitual.\r\nINGREDIENTES: ALCOHOL, CETYL ALCOHOL, CETRIMONIUM CHLORIDE, LAURYL ALCOHOL, PROPYLENE GLYCOL, MYRISTYL ALCOHOL, QUATERNIUM-70, FRAGRANCE (PARFUM), ETHYLHEXYL METHOXYCINNAMATE, ETHYLHEXYL SALICYLATE, HYDROLYZED MILK PROTEIN, BUTYL METHOXYDIBENZOYLMETHANE, CITRIC ACID, HEXYL CINNAMAL, BUTYLPHENYL METHYLPROPIONAL, LINALOOL, BENZYL SALICYLATE, LIMONENE (D-LIMONENE), YELLOW 5 (CI 19140).\r\n\r\nPRESENTACIÓN: Caja x 12 und – 15ml c/u.', 'es'),
(66, 33, 'SHOCK REPARACIÓN INTENSA', 'It is an intensive hair treatment for damaged or mistreated hair. Moisturizes and deeply conditions the hair, facilitating combing, providing shine and softness. Thanks to the Placenta Protein, it reduces the formation of brittle ends and prevents damage caused by sunlight, salinity, the environment and the excessive heat provided by drying, ironing and straightening.\r\n\r\nINSTRUCTIONS FOR USE: It is suggested to use the Intense Shock Repair Treatment twice a week during the first month; then use 1 seminal vial.\r\n1.-Wash the hair with shampoo and dry with a towel. 2.-Pour a dose of the Deep Hydration shock in 60mL of water. 3.-Mix until obtaining a soft and smooth cream. 4.-Apply it by spreading it on the hair from the middle to the end, until it is completely distributed. Let act for 5 to 10 minutes. 5.-Rinse gently with plenty of water and comb as usual.\r\nINGREDIENTS: ALCOHOL, CETYL ALCOHOL, Cetrimonium CHLORIDE, LAURYL ALCOHOL, PROPYLENE GLYCOL, Myristyl Alcohol, Quaternium-70, FRAGRANCE (PARFUM), ETHYLHEXYL METHOXYCINNAMATE, ETHYLHEXYL SALICYLATE, HYDROLYZED MILK PROTEIN, BUTYL METHOXYDIBENZOYLMETHANE, CITRIC ACID HEXYL cinnamal, butylphenyl methylpropional, LINALOOL, BENZYL SALICYLATE, LIMONENE (D-LIMONENE), YELLOW 5 (CI 19140).\r\n\r\nPRESENTATION: Box x 12 und – 15ml each.', 'en'),
(67, 34, 'SHOCK PROTECCIÓN COLOR', 'Es un tratamiento protector de los cabellos tinturados que están constantemente expuestos a los rayos solares. Desarrollada especialmente para proteger el color, acondicionar y equilibrar la estructura de cabellos teñidos. La incorporación de la Proteína de Seda protege al cabello de las agresiones del medio ambiente. Especial para cabellos teñidos, permanentados y dañados. El cabello lucirá sano, sedoso y con brillo.\r\n\r\nMODO DE USO: Se sugiere el uso del Tratamiento Shock Control Caída 2 veces a la semana durante el primer mes; luego utilizar 1 ampolla seminal. \r\n1.-Lavar el cabello con shampoo y secar con una toalla. 2.-Vierta una dosis del shock Hidratación Profunda en 60mL de agua. 3.-Mezcle hasta obtener una crema suave y tersa. 4.-Aplique esparciéndola en el cabello de medios a punta, hasta lograr su total distribución. Deje actuar de 5 a 10 minutos. 5.-Enjuague suavemente, con abundante agua y proceda con el peinado en forma habitual.\r\nINGREDIENTES: ALCOHOL, CETYL ALCOHOL, CETRIMONIUM CHLORIDE, LAURYL ALCOHOL, PROPYLENE GLYCOL, MYRISTYL ALCOHOL, QUATERNIUM-70, FRAGRANCE (PARFUM), ETHYLHEXYL METHOXYCINNAMATE, ETHYLHEXYL SALICYLATE, HYDROLYZED SILK, BUTYL METHOXYDIBENZOYLMETHANE, CITRIC ACID, HEXYL CINNAMAL, BUTYLPHENYL METHYLPROPIONAL, LINALOOL, BENZYL SALICYLATE, LIMONENE (D-LIMONENE), YELLOW 6 (CI 15985), RED 40 (CI 16035).\r\n\r\nPRESENTACIÓN: Caja x 12 und – 15ml c/u.', 'es'),
(68, 34, 'SHOCK PROTECCIÓN COLOR', 'It is a protective treatment for dyed hair that is constantly exposed to sunlight. Specially developed to protect colour, condition and balance the structure of colored hair. The incorporation of the Silk Protein protects the hair from the aggressions of the environment. Special for dyed, permed and damaged hair. Hair will look healthy, silky and shiny.\r\n\r\nINSTRUCTIONS FOR USE: It is suggested to use the Shock Control Fall Treatment twice a week during the first month; then use 1 seminal vial.\r\n1.-Wash the hair with shampoo and dry with a towel. 2.-Pour a dose of the Deep Hydration shock in 60mL of water. 3.-Mix until obtaining a soft and smooth cream. 4.-Apply it by spreading it on the hair from the middle to the end, until it is completely distributed. Let act for 5 to 10 minutes. 5.-Rinse gently with plenty of water and comb as usual.\r\nINGREDIENTS: ALCOHOL, CETYL ALCOHOL, Cetrimonium CHLORIDE, LAURYL ALCOHOL, PROPYLENE GLYCOL, Myristyl Alcohol, Quaternium-70, FRAGRANCE (PARFUM), ETHYLHEXYL METHOXYCINNAMATE, ETHYLHEXYL SALICYLATE, HYDROLYZED SILK, BUTYL METHOXYDIBENZOYLMETHANE, CITRIC ACID HEXYL cinnamal, butylphenyl methylpropional, linalool , BENZYL SALICYLATE, LIMONENE (D-LIMONENE), YELLOW 6 (CI 15985), RED 40 (CI 16035).\r\n\r\nPRESENTATION: Box x 12 und – 15ml each.', 'en'),
(69, 35, 'SHOCK CONTROL CAIDA', 'Es un tratamiento fortalecedor y revitalizante del cuero cabelludo y cabello, formulado con Extracto de Ginseng, conocido extracto natural que ayuda a disminuir la caída de cabello favoreciendo su crecimiento. Sus componentes energizan y nutren el cabello otorgándole elasticidad y brillo.\r\n\r\nMODO DE USO: Se sugiere el uso del Tratamiento Shock Control Caída 2 veces a la semana durante el primer mes; luego utilizar 1 ampolla seminal. \r\n1.-Lavar el cabello con shampoo y secar con una toalla. 2.-Vierta una dosis del shock Hidratación Profunda en 60mL de agua. 3.-Mezcle hasta obtener una crema suave y tersa. 4.-Aplique esparciéndola en el cabello de medios a punta, hasta lograr su total distribución. Deje actuar de 5 a 10 minutos. 5.-Enjuague suavemente, con abundante agua y proceda con el peinado en forma habitual.\r\nINGREDIENTES: ALCOHOL, CETYL ALCOHOL, CETRIMONIUM CHLORIDE, LAURYL ALCOHOL, PROPYLENE GLYCOL, MYRISTYL ALCOHOL, QUATERNIUM-70, FRAGRANCE (PARFUM), ETHYLHEXYL METHOXYCINNAMATE, ETHYLHEXYL SALICYLATE, PANAX GINSENG ROOT EXTRACT, BUTYL METHOXYDIBENZOYLMETHANE, CITRIC ACID, HEXYL CINNAMAL, BUTYLPHENYL METHYLPROPIONAL, LINALOOL, BENZYL SALICYLATE, LIMONENE (D-LIMONENE), YELLOW 5 (CI 19140), BLUE 1 (CI 42090).\r\n\r\nPRESENTACIÓN: Caja x 12 und – 15ml c/u.', 'es'),
(70, 35, 'SHOCK CONTROL CAIDA', 'It is a strengthening and revitalizing treatment for the scalp and hair, formulated with Ginseng Extract, a well-known natural extract that helps reduce hair loss by promoting its growth. Its components energize and nourish the hair, giving it elasticity and shine.\r\n\r\nINSTRUCTIONS FOR USE: It is suggested to use the Shock Control Fall Treatment twice a week during the first month; then use 1 seminal vial.\r\n1.-Wash the hair with shampoo and dry with a towel. 2.-Pour a dose of the Deep Hydration shock in 60mL of water. 3.-Mix until obtaining a soft and smooth cream. 4.-Apply it by spreading it on the hair from the middle to the end, until it is completely distributed. Let act for 5 to 10 minutes. 5.-Rinse gently with plenty of water and comb as usual.\r\nINGREDIENTS: ALCOHOL, CETYL ALCOHOL, Cetrimonium CHLORIDE, LAURYL ALCOHOL, PROPYLENE GLYCOL, Myristyl Alcohol, Quaternium-70, FRAGRANCE (PARFUM), ETHYLHEXYL METHOXYCINNAMATE, ETHYLHEXYL SALICYLATE, PANAX GINSENG ROOT EXTRACT, BUTYL METHOXYDIBENZOYLMETHANE, CITRIC ACID HEXYL cinnamal, butylphenyl methylpropional , LINALOOL, BENZYL SALICYLATE, LIMONENE (D-LIMONENE), YELLOW 5 (CI 19140), BLUE 1 (CI 42090).\r\n\r\nPRESENTATION: Box x 12 und – 15ml each.', 'en'),
(71, 36, 'BB-TOX PRO TREATMENT', 'La Nueva Nanotecnología BB-TOX permite que los ingredientes naturales de la formulación actúen en lo más profundo de la hebra, logrando un efecto más potente sobre el cabello. La segunda gran ventaja es la reducción del tiempo de aplicación porque las moléculas diminutas son más ligeras y el cabello las absorbe con mayor rapidez. Reduce el volumen del cabello sin alterar su estructura natural. Refuerza, repara y reconstruye con mayor intensidad sobre las zonas dañadas. Brinda suavidad y movimiento en medios y flexibilidad en las puntas. Cabello sin frizz, sedoso y brillante. \r\n\r\nMODO DE USO: \r\n1.Lavar con shampoo alcalino o neutro para limpiar y retirar residuos. De ser necesario, realizar un 2do lavado para una óptima limpieza.\r\nEn cabellos vírgenes, gruesos y rebeldes aplicar un segundo lavado para abrir cutícula, dejando reposar el producto por 5 minutos.\r\nSecar el cabello. Procesados al 50%. Vírgenes, gruesos y rebeldes al 100% (porcentaje promedio previo diagnóstico). \r\n2. Aplicar BB-TOX PRO TREATMENT dejando un centímetro de la raíz hacia las puntas y dejar actuar el producto según los tiempos estimados al tipo de cabello. Procesados: 20 minutos. Vírgenes, gruesos y rebeldes: 30 minutos (tiempo promedio previo diagnóstico).\r\n3. Enjuagar el 100% del producto con agua temperada. Aplicar mascarilla SMOOTHING MASK POST LISS de medios a puntas por 15 minutos para proceder con el sellado. Enjuagar y secar.\r\n4. Cepillar el cabello dividiéndolo en 3 cuadrante. \r\n5. Planchar el cabello dividiéndolo en 4 cuadrantes en mechas finas. Repetir la acción de 3 a 5 veces por mechón. Peinar y aplicar SMOOTHING SERUM POST LISS para finalizar el proceso.\r\n\r\nINGREDIENTES: WATER (AQUA), GLYOXYLIC ACID, DIMETHICONE, CETYL ALCOHOL, GLYCERIN, BEHENTRIMONIUM METHOSULFATE, MACADAMIA TERNIFOLIA SEED OIL, COMMIPHORA MYRRHA RESIN EXTRACT, BEHENTRIMONIUM CHLORIDE, FRAGRANCE (PARFUM), PROPOLIS EXTRACT, BIS-CETEARYL AMODIMETHICONE, STEARYL ALCOHOL, DIMETHICONOL, BUTYLENE GLYCOL, COCOS NUCIFERA (COCONUT) OIL, POLYQUATERNIUM -55, CETEARETH-20, HYDROLYZED KERATIN, BEESWAX, CARBOCYSTEINE, HYDROLYZED HYALURONIC ACID, CANDELILLA CERA, METHYLCHLOROISOTHIAZOLINONE, METHYLISOTHIAZOLINONE.\r\n\r\nPRESENTACIÓN: Pote x 500gr / 1Kg.', 'es'),
(72, 36, 'BB-TOX PRO TREATMENT', 'The New BB-TOX Nanotechnology allows the natural ingredients of the formulation to act in the depths of the strand, achieving a more powerful effect on the hair. The second big advantage is the reduction in application time because the tiny molecules are lighter and are absorbed more quickly by the hair. Reduces hair volume without altering its natural structure. Strengthens, repairs and rebuilds with greater intensity on damaged areas. Provides softness and movement in the middle and flexibility in the ends. Frizz-free, silky and shiny hair.\r\n\r\nMODE OF USE:\r\n1. Wash with alkaline or neutral shampoo to clean and remove residue. If necessary, perform a 2nd wash for optimal cleaning.\r\nIn virgin, thick and rebellious hair, apply a second wash to open the cuticle, leaving the product to rest for 5 minutes.\r\nDry hair. Processed at 50%. Virgins, thick and rebellious at 100% (average percentage prior to diagnosis).\r\n2. Apply BB-TOX PRO TREATMENT leaving a centimeter from the root to the ends and leave the product to act according to the times estimated for the type of hair. Processed: 20 minutes. Virgins, thick and rebellious: 30 minutes (average time prior to diagnosis).\r\n3. Rinse 100% of the product with warm water. Apply SMOOTHING MASK POST LISS from mid-lengths to ends for 15 minutes to proceed with sealing. Rinse and dry.\r\n4. Brush the hair dividing it into 3 quadrants.\r\n5. Flat iron the hair, dividing it into 4 quadrants into thin sections. Repeat the action 3 to 5 times per lock. Comb and apply SMOOTHING SERUM POST LISS to finish the process.\r\n\r\nINGREDIENTS: WATER (AQUA), GLYOXYLIC ACID, DIMETHICONE, CETYL ALCOHOL, GLYCERIN, BEHENTRIMONIUM METHOSULFATE, MACADAMIA TERNIFOLIA SEED OIL, COMMIPHORA MYRRHA RESIN EXTRACT, BEHENTRIMONIUM CHLORIDE, FRAGRANCE (PARFUM), PROPOLIS EXTRACT, BIS-CETEARYL AMODIMETHICONE, STEARYL ALCONE , BUTYLENE GLYCOL, COCOS NUCIFERA (COCONUT) OIL, POLYQUATERNIUM -55, CETEARETH-20, HYDROLYZED KERATIN, BEESWAX, CARBOCYSTEINE, HYDROLYZED HYALURONIC ACID, CANDELILLA CERA, METHYLCHLOROISOTHIAZOLINONE, METHYLISOTHIAZOLINONE.\r\n\r\nPRESENTATION: Pot x 500gr / 1Kg.', 'en'),
(73, 37, 'BB-TOX PRO TREATMENT BLUE', 'Nueva Nanotecnología BB-TOX permite que los ingredientes naturales de la formulación actúen en lo más profundo de la hebra capilar logrando un efecto más potente sobre el cabello. Además, reduce el tiempo de aplicación porque las moléculas son más ligeras y el cabello las absorbe con mayor rapidez. Elimina tonos cobrizos y amarillos oxidados, gracias a los Pigmentos Violetas de su formulación, que ayudan a matizar, neutralizar y prevenir la aparición de los visos rojizos y amarillos no deseados para un rubio perfecto y platinado. Realza el brillo y suavidad de los cabellos rubios y decolorados. Reduce el volumen del cabello sin alterar su estructura natural. Refuerza, repara y reconstruye con mayor intensidad sobre las zonas dañadas. Brinda suavidad y movimiento en la parte media del cabello y flexibilidad en las puntas. Cabello sin frizz, sedoso y brillante. \r\n\r\nMODO DE USO:\r\n1.Lavar con shampoo alcalino o neutro para limpiar y retirar residuos. De ser necesario, realizar un 2do lavado para una óptima limpieza.\r\nEn cabellos vírgenes, gruesos y rebeldes aplicar un segundo lavado para abrir cutícula, dejando reposar el producto por 5 minutos.\r\nSecar el cabello. Procesados al 50%. Vírgenes, gruesos y rebeldes al 100% (porcentaje promedio previo diagnóstico). \r\n2. Aplicar BB-TOX PRO TREATMENT BLUE dejando un centímetro de la raíz hacia las puntas y dejar actuar el producto según los tiempos estimados al tipo de cabello. Procesados: 20 minutos. Vírgenes, gruesos y rebeldes: 30 minutos (tiempo promedio previo diagnóstico).\r\n3. Enjuagar el 100% del producto con agua temperada. Aplicar SEALER BALM BLUE de medios a puntas por 15 minutos para proceder con el sellado. Enjuagar y secar.\r\n4. Cepillar el cabello dividiéndolo en 3 cuadrante. \r\n5. Planchar el cabello dividiéndolo en 4 cuadrantes en mechas finas. Repetir la acción de 3 a 5 veces por mechón. Peinar y aplicar SMOOTHING SERUM POST LISS para finalizar el proceso.\r\n\r\nINGREDIENTES: WATER (AQUA), GLYOXYLIC ACID, DIMETHICONE, CETYL ALCOHOL, GLYCERIN, BEHENTRIMONIUM METHOSULFATE, MACADAMIA TERNIFOLIA SEED OIL, COMMIPHORA MYRRHA RESIN EXTRACT, BEHENTRIMONIUM CHLORIDE, FRAGRANCE(PARFUM), PROPOLIS EXTRACT, BIS-CETEARYL AMODIMETHICONE, STEARYL ALCOHOL, DIMETHICONOL, BUTYLENE GLYCOL, COCOS NUCIFERA (COCONUT) OIL, POLYQUATERNIUM -55, CETEARETH-20, HYDROLYZED KERATIN, D&C Violet N°2 ( CI 60730), BEESWAX, CARBOCYSTEINE, HYDROLYZED HYALURONIC ACID, CANDELILLA CERA, METHYLCHLOROISOTHIAZOLINONE, METHYLISOTHIAZOLINONE.\r\n\r\nPRESENTACIÓN: Pote x 500gr / 1Kg.', 'es'),
(74, 37, 'BB-TOX PRO TREATMENT BLUE', 'New BB-TOX Nanotechnology allows the natural ingredients of the formulation to act in the depths of the hair strand, achieving a more powerful effect on the hair. In addition, it reduces the application time because the molecules are lighter and the hair absorbs them more quickly. Eliminates coppery and rusty yellow tones, thanks to the Violet Pigments in its formulation, which help to nuance, neutralize and prevent the appearance of unwanted reddish and yellow hues for a perfect platinum blonde. Enhances the shine and softness of blonde and bleached hair. Reduces hair volume without altering its natural structure. Strengthens, repairs and rebuilds with greater intensity on damaged areas. Provides softness and movement in the middle part of the hair and flexibility in the ends. Frizz-free, silky and shiny hair.\r\n\r\nMODE OF USE:\r\n1. Wash with alkaline or neutral shampoo to clean and remove residue. If necessary, perform a 2nd wash for optimal cleaning.\r\nIn virgin, thick and rebellious hair, apply a second wash to open the cuticle, leaving the product to rest for 5 minutes.\r\nDry hair. Processed at 50%. Virgins, thick and rebellious at 100% (average percentage prior to diagnosis).\r\n2. Apply BB-TOX PRO TREATMENT BLUE leaving a centimeter from the root to the ends and leave the product to act according to the times estimated for the type of hair. Processed: 20 minutes. Virgins, thick and rebellious: 30 minutes (average time prior to diagnosis).\r\n3. Rinse 100% of the product with warm water. Apply SEALER BALM BLUE from mid-lengths to ends for 15 minutes to proceed with sealing. Rinse and dry.\r\n4. Brush the hair dividing it into 3 quadrants.\r\n5. Flat iron the hair, dividing it into 4 quadrants into thin sections. Repeat the action 3 to 5 times per lock. Comb and apply SMOOTHING SERUM POST LISS to finish the process.\r\n\r\nINGREDIENTS: WATER (AQUA), GLYOXYLIC ACID, DIMETHICONE, CETYL ALCOHOL, GLYCERIN, BEHENTRIMONIUM METHOSULFATE, MACADAMIA TERNIFOLIA SEED OIL, COMMIPHORA MYRRHA RESIN EXTRACT, BEHENTRIMONIUM CHLORIDE, FRAGRANCE(PARFUM), PROPOLIS EXTRACT, BIS-CETEARYL AMODIMETHOL, DIOLSTEARYL ALCONE , BUTYLENE GLYCOL, COCOS NUCIFERA (COCONUT) OIL, POLYQUATERNIUM -55, CETEARETH-20, HYDROLYZED KERATIN, D&C Violet N°2 (CI 60730), BEESWAX, CARBOCYSTEINE, HYDROLYZED HYALURONIC ACID, CANDELILLA CERA, METHYLCHLOROISOTHIAZOLINONE, METHYLISOTHIAZOLINONE.\r\n\r\nPRESENTATION: Pot x 500gr / 1Kg.', 'en'),
(75, 38, 'SEALER BALM BLUE', 'El tratamiento intensivo RADIANT SEALER BALM BLUE contiene pigmentos violetas y la tecnología BBTOX BLUE que actúan  reparando el daño de la hebra capilar. Restaura, hidrata, nutre, y sella cutículas, mejorando la apariencia de los cabellos grises, rubios y decolorados. Neutraliza y matiza los tonos amarillos y rojizos no deseados. Permite un efecto platinado, sedoso, brillante y sin frizz por mas tiempo. Sin sal, Sulfatos ni Parabenos.\r\n\r\nMODO DE USO: Después de aplicar el tratamiento RADIANT BB-TOX PRO TREATMENT BLUE, enjuagar el cabello y aplicar RADIANT SEALER BALM BLUE sobre todo el cabello mojado de medios a puntas. Dejar actuar por 15 minutos, luego enjuagar con agua tibia. Secar al 100% con la ayuda de una secadora y cepillo. Pasar la plancha mecha por mecha de 4 a 5 veces. Si el cabello es delgado, exponerlo a una temperatura de 180°C y si el cabello  es grueso exponerlo a una temperatura de 200°C.\r\n\r\nINGREDIENTES: WATER (AQUA), CETYL ALCOHOL, STEARYL ALCOHOL,GLYCERIN, CETEARYL ALCOHOL,DIMETHICONE, BEHENTRIMONIUM METHOSULFATE, CETRIMONIUM CHLORIDE, AMODIMETHICONE, FRAGRANCE (PARFUM), BUTYLENE GLYCOL, CITRIC ACID, BENZYL ALCOHOL, COCOS NUCIFERA (COCONUT)OIL, PCA DIMETHICONE, POLYQUATERNIUM-55, HYDROLYZED  KERATIN, D&C VIOLET N°2 (CI 60730), TRIDECETH-12, POLYSORBATE 20, HYDROLYZED HYALURONIC ACID, METHYLCHLOROISOTHIAZOLINONE, METHYLISOTHIAZOLINONE.\r\n\r\nPRESENTACIÓN: Frasco x 1Lt.', 'es'),
(76, 38, 'SEALER BALM BLUE', 'The RADIANT SEALER BALM BLUE intensive treatment contains violet pigments and BBTOX BLUE technology that act by repairing damage to the hair strand. Restores, hydrates, nourishes, and seals cuticles, improving the appearance of gray, blonde, and bleached hair. Neutralizes and nuances unwanted yellow and reddish tones. Allows a platinum, silky, shiny and frizz-free effect for longer. No salt, sulfates or parabens.\r\n\r\nHOW TO USE: After applying the RADIANT BB-TOX PRO TREATMENT BLUE treatment, rinse hair and apply RADIANT SEALER BALM BLUE all over wet hair from mid-lengths to ends. Leave on for 15 minutes, then rinse with warm water. Dry 100% with the help of a dryer and brush. Pass the iron wick by wick 4 to 5 times. If the hair is thin, expose it to a temperature of 180°C and if the hair is thick, expose it to a temperature of 200°C.\r\n\r\nINGREDIENTS: WATER (AQUA), CETYL ALCOHOL, STEARYL ALCOHOL,GLYCERIN, CETEARYL ALCOHOL,DIMETHICONE, BEHENTRIMONIUM METHOSULFATE, CETRIMONIUM CHLORIDE, AMODIMETHICONE, FRAGRANCE (PARFUM), BUTYLENE GLYCOL, CITRIC ACID, BENZYL ALCOHOL, COCOS NUCIFERA (COCONUT)OIL, PCAHOL DIMETHICONE, POLYQUATERNIUM-55, HYDROLYZED KERATIN, D&C VIOLET N°2 (CI 60730), TRIDECETH-12, POLYSORBATE 20, HYDROLYZED HYALURONIC ACID, METHYLCHLOROISOTHIAZOLINONE, METHYLISOTHIAZOLINONE.\r\n\r\nPRESENTATION: Bottle x 1Lt.', 'en');
